casebody.data:
James J. BAKER
v.
Lisa WHITNUM-BAKER. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 15, 2016. Lisa Whitnum-Baker, self-represented, in support of the petition. Tara Dugo, in opposition.

The defendant's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 163 Conn.App. 903 , 132 A.3d 1106 (2016) (AC 37614/AC 37615/AC 37616/AC 37617/AC 37618/AC 37619), is denied.
